description:
Great British Menu - Season 11, Episodes 31 to 35




North East

Mini Patel is back for a second attempt at the north east regional title, but he is competing against two young newcomers - Tommy Banks and Chris Archer. Tommy Banks is 26 and is a self- taught chef who already has a Michelin star. Chris Archer is another competitive young chef who is creating an entirely gold dish - hoping for a gold-star score as well.




Original Air Dates: 10-Oct-2016 to 14-Oct-2016
